1 0 0 1 72 710 Tm
(CODEX VERIFICATION AGENT FOR RTL TESTBENCH GENERATION) Tj
T*
(MINI PROJECT 2 ? PHASE 2) Tj
T*
(TOPIC 2: AI FOR DESIGN VERIFICATION) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This project implements a Codex-based verification agent that reads a natural-language RTL) Tj
T*
(specification and a set of candidate Verilog implementations, generates a self-checking) Tj
T*
(Verilog testbench, and evaluates that testbench through simulation. The goal is to) Tj
T*
(automatically isolate the single correct RTL implementation among buggy mutants.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. METHODOLOGY & PROBLEM DEFINITION) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(We address the Google verification-style ICLAD task. Each problem contains:) Tj
T*
(? a natural-language specification \(specification.md\)) Tj
T*
(? multiple candidate RTL implementations \(mutant_*.v\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Only one RTL implementation is correct. The agent must generate a Verilog testbench that) Tj
T*
(passes only the correct design.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The scoring metric is:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Score = 1 / \(number of passing implementations\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(If the correct implementation fails the testbench, the score is 0. The ideal result is 1.0,) Tj
T*
(meaning exactly one implementation passes.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Our methodology is a structured generate-evaluate-refine workflow:) Tj
T*
(1. parse the specification into structured JSON) Tj
T*
(2. build a test plan) Tj
T*
(3. generate a self-checking Verilog testbench) Tj
T*
(4. run simulation on all candidate RTL implementations) Tj
T*
(5. refine if the result is not discriminating enough) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This approach is suitable because the task requires behavioral precision, not just) Tj
T*
(syntactically valid code generation.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2. AGENT ARCHITECTURE \(COMPONENTS, DESIGN, DIFFERENCES FROM PROMPTING\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The repository is organized as a concrete agent workspace:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(verification-agent/) Tj
T*
(??? AGENTS.md) Tj
T*
(??? agent.py) Tj
T*
(??? run_pipeline.py) Tj
T*
(??? run_sim.py) Tj
T*
(??? spec_parser.py) Tj
T*
(??? tb_generator.py) Tj
T*
(??? simulator.py) Tj
T*
(??? prompts/) Tj
T*
(??? sample_problem/) Tj
T*
(??? tb/) Tj
T*
(??? artifacts/) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Main components:) Tj
T*
(? agent.py: orchestrates parsing, planning, generation, simulation, and refinement) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
