BT
/F1 10 Tf
12 TL
1 0 0 1 72 710 Tm
(? generating good first-pass testbenches for simpler combinational problems) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Where AI is weaker:) Tj
T*
(? strict tool-compatibility details) Tj
T*
(? edge cases involving complex packed-vector indexing) Tj
T*
(? consistently generating simulator-safe Verilog for all interface styles) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This means AI is effective for reasoning and candidate generation, but it still benefits) Tj
T*
(from deterministic constraints and execution-based validation.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(9. CHALLENGES, LIMITATIONS, IMPROVEMENTS) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Key challenges:) Tj
T*
(? LLM timeouts on large prompts) Tj
T*
(? invisible progress during long generations) Tj
T*
(? generated testbenches missing timing-specific checks) Tj
T*
(? generated Verilog that compiles poorly on some interface patterns) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Fixes implemented in this phase:) Tj
T*
(? configurable Codex timeout) Tj
T*
(? prompt compaction) Tj
T*
(? line-buffered logging) Tj
T*
(? deterministic synchronous-reset guard) Tj
T*
(? iverilog -g2012 compilation support) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Main limitations:) Tj
T*
(? not yet evaluated on the full visible benchmark set) Tj
T*
(? not yet robust across all vectorized module shapes) Tj
T*
(? refinement still depends partly on prompt behavior) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Phase 3 improvements:) Tj
T*
(? run the full visible benchmark set) Tj
T*
(? collect aggregate metrics) Tj
T*
(? strengthen deterministic testbench post-processing) Tj
T*
(? improve refinement on failing compile cases) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(10. CONCRETE OUTPUTS AND REPRODUCIBILITY) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The agent produces explicit artifacts, including:) Tj
T*
(? generated testbenches under tb/) Tj
T*
(? parsed specifications under artifacts/<problem>/parsed_spec.json) Tj
T*
(? test plans under artifacts/<problem>/test_plan.json) Tj
T*
(? simulation summaries under artifacts/<problem>/iteration_1_results.json) Tj
T*
(? final results under artifacts/<problem>/final_result.json) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The complete workflow is reproducible with one command:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(python3 run_pipeline.py --problem-dir sample_problem --max-iters 1) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Real benchmark result artifacts for enc_bin2gray, enc_bin2onehot, and shift_right are) Tj
T*
(included in the submission package.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(11. SUMMARY) Tj
T*
() Tj
ET
endstream
